channel.title: Compilers
channel.itunes:author: Alex Aiken
channel.itunes:summary: This course will discuss the major ideas used today in the implementation of programming language compilers. You will learn how a program written in a high-level language designed for humans is systematically translated into a program written in low-level assembly more suited to machines!
